.part1").hide();\r\n\theadarea3.show();\r\n}else .part1").hide();\r\n\theadarea4.show();\r\n}else{\r\n\theadarea1.show();\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n/*switch (hltype) {\r\n\tcase 2:\r\n\t\t//\xe5\xa4\xb4\xe6\x9d\xa1\xe5\x8f\xaf2\xe8\xa1\x8c\xe6\x88\x96\xe6\x9b\xb4\xe5\xa4\x9a\xef\xbc\x8c\xe5\x8f\xb3\xe4\xbe\xa7\xe6\x9c\x89\xe4\xb8\x93\xe9\xa2\x98\xe5\x9b\xbe\r\n\t\theadarea1.hide();\r\n\t\theadarea2.hide();\r\n\t\theadarea3.show();\r\n\t\tbreak\r\n\tdefault:\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\tbreak\r\n}*/\r\n\r\n\r\n               \r\n\r\n/* \xe4\xbe\xaf \xe5\xa4\xb4\xe6\x9d\xa1\xe4\xbb\xa3\xe7\xa0\x81\r\n\r\n! function(window, document) {\r\n                   (function() {\r\n                       if                 //\xe6\x91\x98\xe8\xa6\x81\xe6\x96\x87\xe5\xad\x97\xe4\xb8\x8d\xe5\x8f\x98\xef\xbc\x8c\xe6\x9c\x80\xe5\xa4\x9a12px*62\xe4\xb8\xaa\xe6\xb1\x89\xe5\xad\x97\xef\xbc\x9b\r\n                           syhistoryid.setAttribute("class",syhistoryid_class+" font-size-twenty-four");\r\n                           break\r\n                       case 2:\r\n                          // slider($(\'.items\'));\n\n    function slider(elem) {\n        var items = elem.children(),\n                max = items.length - 1,\n                animating = false,\n                currentElem,\n                nextElem,\n                pos = 0;\n\n        sync();\n\n        return {\n            next: function () {\n                move(1);\n            },\n            prev: function () {\n                move(-1);\n            },\n            itemsNum: items && items.length\n        };\n\n        function move(dir) {\n            if (animating) {\n                return;\n            }\n            if (dir > 0 && pos == max || dir < 0 && pos == 0) {\n                if (dir > 0) {\n                    nextElem = elem.children(\'div\').first().remove();\n                    nextElem.hide();\n                    elem.append(nextElem);\n                } else {\n                    nextElem = elem.children(\'div\').last().remove();\n                    nextElem.hide();\n                    elem.prepend(nextElem);\n                }\n                pos -= dir;\n                sync();\n            }\n            animating = true;\n            items = elem.children();\n            currentElem = items[pos + dir];\n            $(currentElem).fadeIn(400, function () {\n                pos += dir;\n                animating = false;\n            });\n        }\n\n        function sync() {\n            items = elem.children();\n            for (var i = 0; i < items.length; ++i) {\n                items[i].style.display = i == pos ? \'block\' : \'\';\n            }\n        }\n\n    }\n\n    if (slideEle.itemsNum && slideEle.itemsNum > 1) {\n        setInterval(function () {\n            slideEle.next();\n        }, 4000)\n    }\n\n\n</script>\n<script>\n    function class="intro_header">\n<h2 class="bui-modal__title">Verified reviews from real guests.</h2>\n<p class="bui-modal__paragraph">We have more than 70 million property reviews, all from <strong>real, verified guests</strong>.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="rlp-intro">\n<div class="rlp-intro__container clearfix">\n<h2 class="rlp-intro__title rlp-intro__a11y-exp-title">How does it work?</h2>\n<ul class="rlp-intro-how a11y_contrast_blue_gray">\n<li class="rlp-intro-how__item fl">\n<div class="rlp-intro-how__container rlp-intro-how__container--tickfull">\n<div class="rlp-intro-how__sub-container">\n<p class="rlp-intro-how__num rlp-intro-how__num--tickfull">1</p>\n<p class="rlp-intro-how__icon bicon-tickfull" aria-hidden="true"></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h3
